        <head>SWEET MAMA</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Everyday of my life, everyday of my life she is still in my mind every day of my life</l>
          <l>Oh sweet mama!</l>
          <l>oh sweet mama!</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>I used to burn up inside, up inside a flock of devils on my side, burn up inside </l>
          <l>Oh sweet mama!</l>
          <l>oh sweet mama!</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I walk away, walk away, i just walk away since that day she passed away, i just walk away</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Oh sweet mama!</l>
          <l>oh sweet mama!</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l> Oh ya mama!</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
